        friendList.add(t.replaceAll(&quot;\\h&quot;, &quot; &quot;));
    }
    Collections.sort(friendList);

The `\h` represents any horizontal whitespace in a Java [regular expression Pattern](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html), which includes the non-breaking space and others.  So we&#39;re going above and beyond the observed problem, normalizing all possible &quot;spaces&quot;.

